Nigeria’s Mayowa Nicholas keeps soaring higher. Gracing the runways in Milan and York, she has yet achieved another feat as she appears in America’s Vogue May 2018 issue. Mayowa Nicholas II American Vogue 2018 She was photographed by Philip -Lorca Dicorcia and styled by Phyllis Posnick. She had earlier featured in Vogue España earlier this year. For its spring/summer 2018 campaign, Net-A-Porter featured her as one of the models for their spring/summer 2018 campaign. Check out her pictures below: